author: wn.com
title: Geert Wilders unveils Senate candidates amid warnings over 'blatant racism'
text: An anti-halal campaigner, a former Army officer and the president of a secretive anti-Islam group are unveiled as the first Senate candidates who will stand for a party set up by controversial Dutch politician Geert Wilders. ...
